sql_json.natural_language: Find the most recent thread that has attachments.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE hasAttachments = true ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
